<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>Image Search API</title>
	<link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="page-header">
			<h1>ImageSearch API Microservice</h1>
		</div>
		<div class="page-header">
			<h3>How to Use:</h3>
		</div>

		<p>1) To search for something, add <b>'/api/imagesearch/'your_search_here'/</b> to end of the url.</p>
		<p></p>
		<p>2) It returns images from a variety of sources</p>

		<div class="page-header">
			<h3>Optional Parameters:</h3>
		</div>
		<li><b>Offset</b> | allows for pagination of results</li>

		<div class="page-header">
			<h3>Example Usage</h3>
		</div>
		<p>To request images:</p>
		<code>https://tranquil-sands-81392.herokuapp.com/api/imagesearch/pokemon</code>
		<br/><br/>
		<p>To request images with a offset:</p>
		<code>https://tranquil-sands-81392.herokuapp.com/api/imagesearch/funny cats?offset=3</code>
		<br/><br/>
		<p>To request all previous searches:</p>
		<code>https://tranquil-sands-81392.herokuapp.com/api/latest/imagesearch</code>

		<div class="page-header">
			<h3>Example Output</h3>
		</div>
		<p>Image Request:</p>
		<code>
			{	
				<br />
				url: "http://i0.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/original/000/492/231/636.jpg",
				<br />
				snippet: "Fluffy White Cat: Image Gallery",
				<br />
				thumbnail:"https://encrypted-tbn0...",
				<br />
				context:"http://knowyourmeme.com/memes/fluffy-white-cat..."
				<br />
			}		
		</code>
		<br /><br />
		<p>ImageSearch Request:</p>
		<code>
			{	
				<br />
				term: "funny cats",
				<br />
				when: "Sun Jul 30 2017 14:11:46 GMT-0400 (Eastern Daylight Time)",
				<br />
				from: "Your approx. location"
				<br />
			}		
		</code>

	</div>
	<div class="space"></div>
	<script
	src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.min.js"
	integrity="sha256-hwg4gsxgFZhOsEEamdOYGBf13FyQuiTwlAQgxVSNgt4="
	crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-Tc5IQib027qvyjSMfHjOMaLkfuWVxZxUPnCJA7l2mCWNIpG9mGCD8wGNIcPD7Txa" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>